content_description: Two young men enjoy a high-speed night drive while hanging out of a car's sunroof and windows, cheering as they pass streetlights.

High.reason: Peak excitement with loud cheering and fast-moving streetlights creating a sense of speed.

Medium.reason: Moderate movement as the subjects look out at the passing scenery with less intense shouting.

Low.reason: Relatively calm opening in lower light before the main action and shouting begins.
